{"tid":403460,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(醫生jj請入) 男人保健問題","createTime":"2017-09-17T08:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T13:49:37.000Z","uid":13032,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"62bc3d11a16f52611f55af71d65fef81484f68e2","tid":403460,"uid":13032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"大概兩日前諗住打丁嗰時發覺<br />\n硬度不佳勃起時間好短<br />\n充血狀態下陰莖根部輕壓即可彎曲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/155339_a4ae96143623151ae994bc432b73bd6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F155339_a4ae96143623151ae994bc432b73bd6a.jpg&h=e7ce46b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過又唔覺得痛 又冇出血<br />\n瞓醒都有晨勃但硬度偏低（60%-78%）<br />\n我上網查過應該是白膜受損或破裂 <br />\n我想問香港有冇醫院可以進行相關手術 <br />\n還是可以自我復原？ <br />\n定係我的個案唔係白膜破裂？<br />\n我同女友最近都冇啪啪啪 <br />\n不過可能有撞倒或者壓過<br />\n認真救鳩post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非gay<br />\n有冇巴打都試過 可以分享下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔知有冇開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為真係唔知邊到問好"},{"pid":"6cad787ef08a497bac4e9d526363dcf57008a743","tid":403460,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:17:42.000Z","msg":"你幾耐出一次精？計曬扑嘢+打丁"},{"pid":"510f6ffd3e87cf5413751d9dc94590f5ffc08994","tid":403460,"uid":13032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你幾耐出一次精？計曬扑嘢+打丁</blockquote><br />\n一兩日出一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15a85b1a71c276a1fd7706d6778567387353473a","tid":403460,"uid":13032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112ee2